summary: This is a fairly simple mod that I wanted but couldn\'t find anywhere. It adds nine spells that will teleport you to any of the major holds.
descriptionHtml:
This is a fairly simple mod that I wanted but couldn\'t find anywhere. It adds nine spells that will teleport you to any of the major holds.
The spells are in the broken building in Winterhold, just to the right of where you fast travel into.
The spells should all have a required Alteration level of 50.

If you appreciate the mod, please endorse it.
author: Elec0
